<div class="container">
    <div class="col-md-12">
        <p>The club is then signposted.
            Follow the road for 400 yards and at the 2nd mini-roundabout turn left into
            Barleylands Road.
            Forest Glade Football Club is situated around 300 yards on the left, adjacent to the
            Recycling Centre
        </p>
